{{wiktionary|puppy}}
'''Puppy''' may refer to: * A pup, being the young of a [[dog]], other canine or some other animal species (such as seals) * By analogy, a young, relatively immature human (boy or girl), especially when considered inexperienced and/or conceited; as in [[puppy pile]] * [[Puppy Linux]], a Live CD Linux distribution * "[[The Puppy Episode]]," an 1997 episode of the TV sitcom ''[[Ellen (TV series)|Ellen]]'' in which Ellen DeGeneres' character comes out of the closet * [[Puppy (album)]], an album by the band Fluke * [[Puppy (film)]], Australian film * [[Jeff_Koons#Puppy_1992|''Puppy'']], a sculpture created by Jeff Koons * [[The Puppies]], a 1990s rap group
